some players even choose this setup. The engine is happy for White, but
Black's position is very solid on the long term}) 8. f3 Be6 9. Nbc3 Qd7 (9...
Bc4 {This is one of the main moves, but I don't like} 10. Bxc4 Nxc4 11. e6 $1 {
