Be3 Qd7 9. Nbc3 O-O-O 10. O-O {White can sacrifice a pawn, but If Black
remembers the theory, he will be fine.} Nxe5 11. Bb5 Nc6 12. h3 (12. Rc1 {
Radek tried this move, but didn't achieve much in the game:} a6 13. Bxc6 Qxc6
14. f3 Bf5 15. Bf4 Rd7 16. d5 Qg6 {1/2 (31)-1/2 (31) Wojtaszek,R (2737)
