Rxd1+ 21. Rxd1 Kxc6 {Black has a structural problem, but his king is very
active and will soon develop all his pieces. The game is about equality.} 22.
Nc4 Be7 23. Kf1 Rd8 24. Rc1 Bg5 25. Re1 Bf6 26. b3 b5 27. Na5+ Kb6 28. b4 Rd6
