since White will not have access to e4} 12. Na4 (12. Qd2 Nxe5 $17) 12... f6 13.
Nc5 (13. Nxb6 axb6 14. Ba4 fxe5 15. Bb5 Qd5 16. Nc3 (16. Qa4 Nxd4 $19) 16...
Qd6 17. Bxc6 bxc6 18. dxe5 Qxd1 19. Rfxd1 Be7 $17 {Espinosa Veloz,E (2516)
